snippet.title: Launch Trailer | Diesel Legacy: The Brazen Age
snippet.description:
Diesel Legacy: The Brazen Age is out now on Xbox X|S!

Diesel Legacy: The Brazen Age introduces a brand-new style of fighting game coming December 3. Engage in 2v2 matches within an innovative 3-lane system against a gorgeous, hand-drawn Dieselpunk backdrop. For more information, visit http://www.diesellegacy.com/

Purchase now at https://www.xbox.com/games/store/diesel-legacy-the-brazen-age/9PL45M93RD9G
